Global Hockey Stick Tapes Market Insights
Hockey Stick Tapes Market size was valued at USD 0.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.45 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Hockey Stick Tapes Market Overview
The global hockey stick tapes market was valued at approximately USD 100 million in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.6% from 2025 to 2030. The market growth is driven by increasing interest in hockey as a sport, rising participation in grassroots hockey, and the continuous innovations in hockey accessories. The demand for high-quality tapes, which offer better grip, durability, and aesthetic appeal, further fuels market expansion. The expansion of online retail and the growing popularity of synthetic cloth tapes over traditional options are also contributing factors.

